---
title: Mediterranean Beef Gyros & Herby Mayo with Spiced Fries & Pickled Onion
description: There’s something about the humble Gyro that seems to stir up passion in people. Maybe it’s the tender beef, or perhaps the joy of having chips and a soft, pillowy wrap to enjoy everything in? Perhaps it’s just the noble nature of the Greeks. Whatever the reason, we’re mighty glad it’s on the menu.
